---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-gray-800 bg-gray-950 mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-lg bg-brand-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs">
            OA
          </div>
          <span class="font-bold text-white">Open Assets</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          Using AI to scale up open asset-level data analysis &mdash; emission estimates, ownership trees, and more.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Data</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/steel/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Steel Sector</a></li>
          <li><a href="/methodology/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Methodology</a></li>
          <li><span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Power (Coming Soon)</span></li>
          <li><span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cement (Coming Soon)</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Attribution -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">About</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          A research collaboration between researchers at the University of Oxford and the University of Queensland,
          using AI to explore methods to scale up asset-level data analysis. Data sources include GEM GIST,
          ClimateTrace, TPI, and company annual reports.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Disclaimer -->
    <div class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-8 pt-8">
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-amber-500/20 bg-amber-500/5 px-4 py-3 mb-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.964-.833-2.732 0L4.082 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-xs text-amber-200/70 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-semibold text-amber-200">Beta.</span>
            This platform is under active development. Data, methodologies, and coverage are preliminary
            and subject to change. All estimates are derived from publicly available sources and
            modelling &mdash; they should not be treated as verified figures. Use at your own discretion.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 text-center">
        &copy; {year} Open Assets. A collaboration between researchers at the University of Oxford and the University of Queensland.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
